    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>■ 关于《罗密欧是个绝命侠》</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款第三人称单人动作冒险游戏中，你将操控主角“罗密欧・观星者”，开启一段分为多个章节的冒险。他的故事充满着未知变数，穿插着激烈战斗，散落着支线任务，玩家可根据自身节奏灵活体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/6f7ba0c27626b3df36b0e279e2c639a9.poster.avif?t=1770733870\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/6f7ba0c27626b3df36b0e279e2c639a9.webm?t=1770733870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/6f7ba0c27626b3df36b0e279e2c639a9.mp4?t=1770733870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>■ 一段跨越时空的故事</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作故事始于一场事件引发的时空碎裂。处在生死边缘的罗密欧被一种全新的超级科技救活。他因此被美国联邦调查局时空警察部招募为特别探员，在宇宙中穿梭，寻找那些趁机为非作歹的罪犯，试图恢复宇宙的秩序。与此同时，他也在寻找失踪女友朱丽叶的线索，很快他发现，她的失踪与时空崩塌之间，或许存在着比他想象中更密切的联系。戴上名为死亡装备的面具后，在时空的边缘，等待罗密欧的会是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/8f3808edd12ea2c51ba8f628064b1228.poster.avif?t=1770733870\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/8f3808edd12ea2c51ba8f628064b1228.webm?t=1770733870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/8f3808edd12ea2c51ba8f628064b1228.mp4?t=1770733870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>■ 以血还血</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗密欧可在刀剑与枪械之间灵活切换作战。击溃挡路的一波波敌人，演绎全新的血腥动作场面，打倒潜伏在前方的可怕时空罪犯。吸收敌人的血液，即可触发罗密欧的特殊攻击：血色夏日，此技能足以扭转任何不利战局。随着剧情推进，罗密欧的各类武器可不断强化与改造，助他应对实力愈发强大的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/8a59cb22ca0d7f739474a0a83df584e1.poster.avif?t=1770733870\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/8a59cb22ca0d7f739474a0a83df584e1.webm?t=1770733870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050900/extras/8a59cb22ca0d7f739474a0a83df584e1.mp4?t=1770733870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>■ Grasshopper Manufacture全新力作！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《罗密欧是个绝命侠》是Grasshopper Manufacture多年来推出的首款全新原创作品！凭借数十年的开发经验，这款充满未知惊喜的新作，必将为玩家带来全新体验！</p>",
